Finally over the shock of another owl branded establishment , my destination was none other than the bohemian West Village and the Little Owl. For a medium sized space, the table coordination and setting is done very well, enough to guarantee a good turnover for the place but yet not too close to be rubbing backs with my elbows. The burger is of a grade A quality mince and other reviewers actually examine the combination that delivers such a flavor, however for all non-cheese fans, I urge you to check the picture and decide whether the quantity of cheese may be a bit too much for your liking...in my case it was! All in all, this is simply another 4 star review reiterating the same ...
